hillip z pace dr chris rowland stephen oglesby randy l wolsey john h pinkerton  mr pinkerton has served as a director for lonestar since august  and became chairman of the board in august  he became a director of range resources corporation nyse rrc in  and was elected chairman of the board of directors of range in   he joined range as president in  and was appointed chief executive officer in   in  mr pinkerton retired as ceo of range and stepped down as chairman on january    mr pinkerton remains a director of range  previously mr pinkerton served in various capacities at snyder oil corporation for twelve years including the position of senior vice president  mr pinkerton received his bachelor of arts degree in business administration from texas christian university where he now serves on the board of trustees and a master’s degree from the university of texas at arlington  during his year tenure range resources grew from its small cap origins to be a  billion dollar enterprise with a preeminent position in the marcellus shale in the usa  as ceo mr pinkerton established the technical expertise to enable a drillingled strategy complemented by bolton acquisitions where synergies would enhance growth  this resulted in a rapid and impressive increase in the scale of the business and seven consecutive years of doubledigit growth in both production and reserves adjusted for debt mr pinkerton has widespread skill in the management acquisition and divestiture of oil and gas properties – including related corporate financing activities – hedging risk analysis and the evaluation of drilling programs  he has represented the industry in policy matters serving on the executive committee of america’s natural gas alliance  he is a us citizen   john m pinkerton  executive bio compensation history and contacts  equilar atlas   log in  sign up x   as featured in john m pinkerton former vp and chief financial officer at aftermarket technology view full profile are you john m pinkert