es with a thorough understanding of the factors that drove the financials this was invaluable to me in being able to sucessfully run our businesses john developed financial models that would be the envy of any company and had a mastery of the puts and takes that drove changes to our financials like no other cfo with whom i have collaborated he drove the budgeting process was vital to our ma reviews developed our secmandated reports and just overall knew the story behind every critical number atc reported john is a topnotch professional suffice to say i am grateful to john for his professional service to atc and feel solidly confident in my recommendation of him for another cfo position any organization would be proud to call john its cfo just as atc was todd peterssee moresee lessjohn made it a point to give his full attention to his colleagues when asked and was always generous in spending his time to discuss issues that would arise he has an outstanding grasp of accounting principles and a knack for understanding the true nature of business issues which helped to speed along the process of resolving complex accounting and financial reporting matterssee moresee lesssign up to see who recommended johngroupssec professionals groupthe cfo leadership council chicagothe financial executives networking group  feng onlinethe cfo alliance an achievenext communitylinked n chicago lincchicago c level cclfinance plus private equity venture capital and ma newssee  moresmall business cfosbrilliant financial searche l i t edigitalcfo  the group for finance  techminded business professionalsthe strategic cfolinked financial professionalsuniversity of wisconsinmilwaukee alumni associationsee lessview john’s full profile tosee who you know in commonget introducedcontact john directlyview john’s full profilenot the john you’re looking for view moreview this profile in another languageenglishgermanpeople also viewedben bloomvice president at snc manufacturing co inckevin j conradcont